[{"location":"#PlutoSlides","page":"Home","title":"PlutoSlides","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"Documentation for PlutoSlides.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"#PlutoSlides.myTitle-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"PlutoSlides.myTitle","text":"myTitle(; title, author, figures, footnote=nothing)\n\nDisplay a formatted title slide for a Pluto presentation.\n\nArguments\n\ntitle: String, HTML, Markdown, etc. content for the main title.\nauthor: String, HTML, Markdown, etc. content for the author and affiliation.\nfigures: Array of Resource objects for logos or images.\nfootnote: Optional Markdown or HTML footnote.\n\nExample\n\nmyTitle(     title=html\"<b>My Presentation</b>\",     author=html\"<center>Jane Doe</center>\",     figures=[Resource(\"logo.png\", :width => 100)] )\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#PlutoSlides.notebook_font_size","page":"Home","title":"PlutoSlides.notebook_font_size","text":"notebook_font_size(fontsize_html=24, fontsize_md=24)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#PlutoSlides.pause-Tuple{Integer}","page":"Home","title":"PlutoSlides.pause","text":"pause(n::Integer)\n\nCreates an invisible numbered pause marker for incremental slide reveals. Mimics beamer's \\pause[n] behavior - content after this marker will be visible starting from fragment n.\n\nArguments\n\nn: Fragment number (1-based) when this content should become visible\n\nExample\n\nmd\"First content is always visible\"\npause(2)\nmd\"This appears on fragment 2\"\npause(4) \nmd\"This appears on fragment 4\"\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#PlutoSlides.pause-Tuple{}","page":"Home","title":"PlutoSlides.pause","text":"pause()\n\nCreates an invisible pause marker for incremental slide reveals. Use this between content elements in your Pluto cells to create step-by-step reveals.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#PlutoUI.LocalResource-Tuple{AbstractString, AbstractString, Vararg{Pair}}","page":"Home","title":"PlutoUI.LocalResource","text":"PlutoUI.LocalResource(dir::AbstractString, path::AbstractString, html_attributes::Pair...)\n\nSearch recursively for path inside directory dir (including all subdirectories) and return PlutoUI.LocalResource(joinpath(found_dir, path)) for the first match. Throws an ArgumentError if not found.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
